      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      static <T> void doesNotHaveClass(Assert<? extends T> $receiver, java.lang.Class<? extends T> jclass)
      Asserts the value does not have the expected java class. This is an exact match, so assert("test").doesNotHaveClass(String::class.java) is fails but assert("test").doesNotHaveClass(Any::class.java) is successful.
